Threaten						KEY:Crimson Scourge ~ Threaten					OUTPUTNAME:Threaten				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary								VISIBLE:YES																																																																																																				DESC:You are a master of shaking the confidence of your foes. When you use the Intimidate skill to demoralize an opponent, you can do so as a move action rather than a standard action. Second, a successful attempt causes the target to be shaken for %1 rounds. Finally, you gain a +2 bonus on any Intimidate check to demoralize an opponent.|max(1,STR)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													BONUS:SKILL|Intimidate (Demoralize opponent)|2																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:93
