Smell of Blood					KEY:Crimson Scourge ~ Smell of Blood				OUTPUTNAME:Smell of Blood			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary								VISIBLE:YES																																																																																																				DESC:You ave acquired an almost animalistic awareness of the world around you. You gain the scent ability and a +3 insight bonus on initiative checks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Scent																																																BONUS:COMBAT|INITIATIVE|CombatAnticipation|3|TYPE=Insight																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:94
