#Urban Savant Abilities
Weapon and Armor Proficiency			KEY:Urban Savant ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency			OUTPUTNAME:Weapon and Armor Proficiency	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality										VISIBLE:YES																																																																																																				DESC:You do not gain any new proficiency with arms or armor. However, if you previously had light armor proficiency and you had arcane spell casting level, you now have the Battle Caster (Light Armor class feature).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:101
Spellcasting					KEY:Urban Savant ~ Spellcasting					OUTPUTNAME:Spellcasting				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality										VISIBLE:YES																																																																																																				DESC:At each level you may advance 1 level in as an arcane spell caster. If you had arcane spells from multiple classes, this can benefit only 1 per level. If you had no previous arcane abilities, this feature offers you no benefit.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:101
Urban Saavy						KEY:Urban Savant ~ Urban Saavy					OUTPUTNAME:Urban Saavy				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary								VISIBLE:YES																																																																																																				DESC:You are an expert on your local community. You can draw upon this to gain certain benefits against the following types of creatures (aberrations, animals, humanoids, monstrous humanoids, oozes, and vermin) that are commonly found in an urban environment. To access this information you make an appropriate Knowledge skill check at DC 15 as a move action. You must be within 60 feet of your target and have line of sight. This ability functions an unlimited number of times per day, but only once per target or group of similar target creatures.	DESC:Strengths - With you check you learn the general combat capabilities of your target (including base attack bonus, AC, and combat related feats).	DESC:Weaknesses - you can learn your opponent's weaknesses including (HD, DR and what overcomes it, and saves)|PREVARGTEQ:UrbanSavantLVL,4	DESC:Methods - you know your foes methods, you can grant yourself and your allies a +1d6 damage bonus on weapon rolls against them for 1 minute. If you roll 25 or more on your check this increases to +2d6. If you roll 35 or more, +3d6.|PREVARGTEQ:UrbanSavantLVL,7	DESC:True Nature - You understand your targets true nature with a successful check. This grants you and your allies within 60 feet a barrier that functions as a protection from chaos/evil/good/law spell granting a +2 bonus to AC & saves. Your caster level for the spell is your Urban Savant level. If you roll 25 or more on your check, the bonus increases to +3 and to +4 if you roll 35 or more.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:101
Urban Empathy					KEY:Urban Savant ~ Urban Empathy					OUTPUTNAME:Urban Empathy			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary								VISIBLE:YES																																																																																																				DESC:You can use your knowledge to improve the attitude of creatures you encounter (as long as they are not mindless). You may make your appropriate Knowledge check in place of a Diplomacy check to influence the starting attitudes of those you encounter in cities. Against animals you may add your Urban Savant level to your check as the druid's wild empathy class feature.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:102
Continuing Education				KEY:Urban Savant ~ Continuing Education				OUTPUTNAME:Continuing Education		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary								VISIBLE:YES																																												DEFINE:ContinuingEducation|0																																																				DESC:You gain a +%1 insight bonus on Knowledge (dungeoneering), Knowledge (local), Knowledge (nature) checks as well as bardic knowledge checks.|ContinuingEducation																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (Dungeoneering),Knowledge (Local),Knowledge (Nature)|ContinuingEducation	BONUS:VAR|BardicKnowledge|ContinuingEducation																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:102
Eyes of the City					KEY:Urban Savant ~ Eyes of the City					OUTPUTNAME:Eyes of the City			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary								VISIBLE:YES																																																																																																				DESC:Your vision has surpassed that of other city-dwelling humans. You gain low-light vision, allowing you to see twice as far as a normal human. If you already had low-light vision, your range doubles.	DESC:You know intuitively how the city should look. While in an urban environment, you can try to see through the deception of any object or creature that is disguising its true appearance. Make a DC 20 Knowledge (arcana) check. If this successeds, you know whether or not the target's appearance is hidden, but not by what or what it's true form is. If you beat DC 30, you know the means (i.e. Disguise skill, magic, natural shapechanging, etc...).  If it is magical, you can attempt a DC 20+spell level Spellcraft check to determine what spell is being used.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				BONUS:VISION|Low-light|1																																			SOURCEPAGE:102
